    "Wang et al.",
    "36, proposed the use of ICEEMDAN decomposition techniques with a modified version of particular swarm optimization (MPSO) for hyper-parameter selection of the SVM model.",
    "The suggested strategy is more suitable for other common approaches for PV power forecasting.",
    "Wang et al.",
    "37, proposed the combination of the variable-weight combination model with ensemble empirical mode decomposition (EEMD) for PV power forecasting."
